fe73\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"MOCK_CHARACTERS|mockCharactersData|listMockCharacters|commitUpdateCharacterMock|listMockUserProfiles|MOCK_USER_PROFILES|MOCK_STORY_PACKAGES|mockWorkbench|CanvasMockGraph|listMockPackages|MOCK_EDITOR_CHARACTERS|ExitEffectsMockList\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"tool_347b9df6-d948-47b2-adcb-9502059fe73\",\"offset\":0}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"tool_347b9df6-d948-47b2-adcb-9502059fe73\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784712881917\"},\"model_call_id\":\"7f9fe896-3fa6-4959-b19d-28a453a3d9db-2-vhtv\",\"session_id\":\"954e254e-59b7-4fbc-b23f-09ac0d6e93a6\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784712881750}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":61,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"tool_c82b3095-ba64-4290-9f6a-59c145c8cbc\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/04-第一幕打错电话-mock拓扑.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"# 第一幕《打错电话》· 画布 mock 拓扑（代码事实）\\n\\n> 正式稿（仓外）：`doubaoSister/.../定稿的故事/1.第一幕初识.md`（标题《打错电话》）。  \\n> 代码：`CanvasMockGraph.ts` + `CanvasMockGraph.edges.ts`。  \\n> 固化：2026-07-22。用户评语：「稍微有点偏差，但是很准确了」。\\n\\n## 1. 包 / 章节展示名\\n\\n| 键 | 当前值 | 说明 |\\n|----|--------|------|\\n| `packageId` | `pkg_memory_bar_1` | **历史 id 未改**（路由/种子兼容）；勿从 id 推断剧情仍是「内存条」 |\\n| 列表 title | `第一幕：打错电话` | `mockWorkbenchData.ts` |\\n| 顶栏 chapterTitle | `第一幕 · 打错电话` | `StoryEditorShell` |\\n| chapter_start.title | 同上 | 画布节点 |\\n| entryCardId | `lanxing_wrong_number` | `packageConfProjection` DEFAULT 种子 |\\n\\n## 2. 卡拓扑（业务理解）\\n\\n```text\\nchapter_start\\n    → card_wrong_number「打错电话」(lanxing, outbound_auto)\\n         exit_callback「挂机后补打」\\n           effects: attach_call_card → lanxing_callback_int [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":63,"content":"{\